Summary: Bright green fireball moving quickly as if it were landing at 45 degree angle
divs: Sighting DetailsOutside having a cigarette looking out over the hills behind my house, and suddenly a bright green flying fireball appeared moving quickly as if landing at about a 45 degree angle, did not look organic, was large and absoultely something that could be explained. We live near Pt. Mugu
